================================================================================
DARK MIR PROJECT README

================================================================================
INSTALL:
	(possibly done)
	svn co http://abadon.no-ip.org/svn/dark_mir/ DarkMIR
	cd DarkMIR

	(so start here)
	make
	make run
	
	./mir -r [number_for_resolution] [-f] abadon.no-ip.org

================================================================================
USE:
	./mir -h	help

================================================================================
CONTROLS:

	UP		speed up
	DOWN	slow down
	LEFT	rotate left
	RIGHT	rotate right
	
	A		shift left
	D		shift right

	CTRL	fire missile
	ALT		fire laser
	SPACE	fire laser


================================================================================
Thanks for playing this Czech game.

email: alexej.x@mail.ru

